original_title: Carie Karavas: Men, Flaws, and Menopause
overview: Tough, street smart, wisecracking stand-up comic, Carie Karavas (Kevin Can Wait), has been taking the NYC comedy club scene by storm, not to mention the entire country. Her tough exterior, along with her hard-hitting style of delivery, keeps audiences constantly on guard for big laughs.
tagline: Carie Karavas can take a hot flash and make it high comic art.
title: Carie Karavas: Men, Flaws, and Menopause
